  						<table border='0' cellpadding='3' cellspacing='0' width='92%'>
	<tr>
	  <td width='100%' bgcolor='#0E024D' class='spti2' align='center'>THE SHADOW FALLS:TWILIGHT CHAPTER 2</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
	  <td width='100%'><font face='verdana' size='2pt'><html>

<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type"
content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage Express 2.0">
<title>Untitled </title>
</head>

<body>

<p><marquee>*(A Thesis of The Cruel Angel), Like an angel that has no sense of mercy..., Rise, young child, to the heavens like a legend... Cold winds, as blue as the sea.Tear open the door to your heart, I see... But unknowing you seem, just staring at me... Standing there smiling serenely. Desperate, for something to touch... A moment of kindness like that in a dream... Your innocent eyes, have yet no idea... Of the path your destiny will follow... But someday you'll become aware of... Everything that you've got behind you... Your wings are for seeking out a new... Future that only you can search for. The cruel angel's thesis bleeds through a portal like your pulsing blood. If you should betray the chapel of your memories, Cruel angel's thesis enters.....through the window of your soul. So, child, stand tall and embrace the fire of the legend. Embracing the universe like a blazing star!</marquee>
</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">-----------------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Chapter 2. Visions of the Past, Journey to
the Future</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">-----------------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Fires leapt about, people were screaming.
Blood and sinew was strewn across the city. Baking in the
scorching heat. It was pandemonium. Flashes leapt out of the
distance and pulverized the city. Entire sections vanishing in an
instant. High above the burning city a figure floats admiring the
destruction. The figure point a hand toward another part of the
city and another deadly flash leapt out turning the section into
nothing. The figure continued to revel in the destruction. </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">A second figure appeared, it was a half-elf
boy with silvery hair., He flew towards the menace only to be
quickly knocked back down to the city. But the boy didn&#146;t
give up and this time he managed to grasp hold of the floating
menace. He began to scream something at the figure, the figure
ignores the boys plea's and struggled to get out of his grasp.
The boy seeing his plea's where falling on deaf ears slapped the
figure as hard as he could.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">----------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Leylia jumped out her bed, tossing the sweat
soaked sheets away. She stumbled to get to her feet, but she the
nightmare had shaken her to the core. Her mind kept flooding her
with the images of death and destruction. The innocent people
being carved in half, their insides being strewn across the
pavement. The nightmare burned at her and she couldn&#146;t take
it, she vomited on the floor. </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">She heard a whimper beside her, she turned
and her pet dog looked at her pitifully. The animal knew she was
hurting and rubbed against her.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Hi puppy...ugh..what a way to start a
day...&#148; Weakly she got up and sat back up her bed. Then for
first time she noticed something wasn&#146;t right. This
wasn&#146;t her bed, or for that matter this wasn&#146;t her
room. It was a cell. One of Felwithe cells at the bottom of the
castle.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Wha..What am I doing here?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">The guard outside noticed that Leylia had
woken up. &#147;So, you&#146;re awake? Good. Now you&#146;ll be
able to face the wrath of the council. Murderer.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Murderer? What are you talking
about!?!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;You dare deny what you did?
They&#146;re all dead because of you! If I wasn&#146;t in his
majesties service. I would.... &#147;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;That&#146;s enough !! You&#146;re
dismissed.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Yes M&#146;lord.&#148; The guard
turned around and headed up the stairs, soon another person
entered.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Father!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Hello Leylia.&#148; The old King
looked pained, and his response was so cold. It brought tears to
Leylia&#146;s eyes.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Why am I here!?!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;.....&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Father.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;My Leylia.. I had so hoped, that you
would never have to experience hardship or suffering. But fate as
it seems, sees other wise.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;What?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Leylia, what was the last thing you
remember?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;I was on my first patrol. I captured
two poachers and was on the way to Kelethin to turn them in. When
I returned, the city was in flames. Someone unknown had attacked
it. I assume one of the leaders noticed me and attacked. We
dueled for a bit, then I blacked out. Next thing I know I'm lying
in a crater. Someone called Silver Mask kills the man I was
fighting. Then I woke up here.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;And you remember nothing after
that?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;No.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;I see. Come with me Leylia.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">-------------------------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">They exited the prison and began to wind
their way up into the castle. Halfway up the castle, they came to
a large hole in the castle. Air blew through the opening and into
the castle freely. Seeing the damage, Leylia turned and gazed
out, only to turn away at what she saw. The proud city of
Felwithe had been devastated. Buildings were in ruins, smoke
bellowed out into the sky. And for once the bustling city was
quiet.....dead quiet.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">They turned away from the hole and entered a
large chamber. It was the Felwithe council Chambers. It was the
first time Leylia had been inside. The Chamber was only place she
had not been allowed to go, it was for her father and his most
trusted aids only. As they entered the Council members locked icy
glares onto Leylia, all except Caerdwill. But he might as well
pierce her heart with a dagger, as he didn&#146;t even look up at
her. He just stared at the table they were seated around.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">The King seated her and then moved around to
the head of the table.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Leylia. The Council is here today too
decide your fate for your crimes against the nation of
Felwithe&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;What crimes have I committed!?!
Father!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;You don&#146;t deserve to call him
that! You traitorous mongrel!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Morgann!!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;You should have killed her when that
spawn of hell defiled our tombs 18 years ago!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Silence! You lose your place
Morgann!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;I will not be silent! Because of your
folly, both our city and Kelethin are in ruins! Even with all of
Faydwer&#146;s help it will take years to rebuild! You should
have listened to me when we had the chance to prevent this!
Because of this demon spawn, Thousands are dead! And who knows
how many more will die if she is allowed to fulfil the
prophecy!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Morgann. You talk too much. We had no
way of knowing if her powers would grow so out of control. We
didn&#146;t even know if she was one that was spoken of by the
myth!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;We shouldn&#146;t have even have even
tempted fate Caerdwill!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;STOP IT! What have I done!?! Why are
you cursing my very existence?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;My Leylia, you saw through the hole in
the castle wall, of what has happened to our city?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Yes&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;The destruction was done by
..You.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">The nightmare was real. I killed all those
people.. I destroyed the city..... How...</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">She began to cry. &#148;I couldn&#146;t
have..theres no way... I'm not that powerful...no one is that
powerful&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Yes you are Leylia.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;Who, said that!?!&#148;
Leylia&#146;s dog hops up on the table.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;Who let that mutt in
here!?!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;Watch who your calling
mutt!&#148; spoke the dog.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;Puppy?&#148; Leylia was in a
state of shock again.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;Reyas.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;Huh?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;Reyas. My name is Reyas.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;How can a puppy be able to
speak?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;I&#146;m a familiar!! Not some
stupid puppy dog! And I really hate it when you call me
puppy.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;???&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;O brother..This is going to take
a while to explain. I am a familiar. I&#146;m like a companion,
except I can amplify your natural powers and I can shapeshift.
And finally as long as the pendant your wearing around your neck
is never destroyed, I cant die. I was bonded to you by your
father to protect you.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;Leylia turned and looked at the King.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;No, not him. Your real
Father.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;My real father?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147; Yes. His name was Raziel.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;My father was the savior of
Kelethin?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;Yes, but that was only a cover
to infiltrate Felwithe. In actuality he was the Hell Lord of
Paineel.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;What?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;The most powerful incarnation of
death and darkness ever known.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;My father was...that..&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;Yep. But your mother was his
exact opposite, she was Arorua.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;The Lost Bearer of the Holy
Sword Masamune?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;&#147;Right again. The Grail Lord of
Felwithe. Between saving Kelethin and this sorry bunch, he and
your mother fell in love and married. Then they left and most to
Paineel where after being like all good couples, you were born.
Only a few weeks later, the goody two shoes of Erudin attacked
Paineel being lead by some outsider. Sadly, the outsider killed
Arorua. Before Raziel went to find the outsider, he returned here
and gave you to the King to keep you safe and out of
trouble...*cough*like that worked, you troublemaker
you*cough*..and he bonded me to you. To protect you and lead you
home to collect your heritage. Unfortunately, whenever I am bond
to some one, My standard form is change to the first thing they
think of. And of course you just had to be thinking of puppies at
that moment........it&#146;s just not fair..first stuck as a
stupid bird, then turned into a dog, didn&#146;t even get a name,
just puppy this!, puppy that!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;I&#146;m sorry ..puppy&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Giving her an exasperated look &#147;I hate
you....&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Reyas....&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">His tail wags &#148; That sounds so
nice..&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;How could I have had the power to do
all this to the city?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Because your a Dragoon&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;A Dragoon?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&quot;..under the blood moon, two children
forged of the purest light and blackest darkness shall been born.
And they shall be known as the Dragoon, masters of Dragon Kind,
the deciders of the fate of Norrath, the heralds of the Twilight.
And one of those mythical children is you Leylia.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;But I couldn&#146;t have..I can&#146;t
be a Dragoon..&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;You are. The fight against
Andregorous, the leader of the attacking force against Kelethin,
awoke some of the latent powers inside you. You blanked out and
your powers took hold. With one attack you created a 600 foot
crater and wiped Kelethin off the map.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;That&#146;s when I woke up and Silver
Mask finished him off.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Yes. Then you passed out again
and....&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;What happened?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;...&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Tell me!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Your latent abilities took hold and
you went bezerk again...&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">----------------------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">The trees where alit, there was nothing left
of the magnificent tree city. A small army dispatched from
Felwithe approaches the remains.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;By the gods! There&#146;s nothing
left!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;What could have done this?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">The army moved in closer, their arms at high
ready. They began to circle around a large crater.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">*(She&#146;s a Killa/Killa Feeling: By Rare
Software, Killer Instinct The Game)</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Look! Inside the crater!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">In the center of the crater a naked form of
a female elf can be seen, encompassed by swirling mana, it
scorches everything that it touches, except for her and small
pendant around her neck. She looks up at the approaching army.
The mana encompassing her reacts violently and she lets out a
scream. She rockets out of the crater and high into the sky.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;What the!! ARCHERS FIRE!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Thousands of arrows fly from within the army
ranks and soar toward her. But they all impact on an invisible
barrier. The girl holds out her hand and a blade of mana forms in
it. She falls like a rock and crashes into the ranks, cutting
dozens in half. Her eyes flash with power and the ranks erupt
into flames as energy swirls from her. </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">A few mounted soldiers escape the attack and
begin to flee. They ride as fast as their mounts will take them.
The girl turns to them as the energy begins to reside, then just
as suddenly she vanishes. The fleeing soldiers never saw her
reappear behind them and blast them into the next life. </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Only a few moments later, the gates of
Felwithe explode sending shrapnel and debris into the city.
Guards began to stream to the city entrance to halt this
assailant. Ready to protect they&#146;re proud city, but their
spirit and bravery diminished rapidly as a single girl cut their
friends and buddies to ribbons. She spread their blood across the
ground as if it were whitewash, and any that tried to flee were
incinerated by bolts of energy.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Finishing of the last of the guards the girl
leapt into the air and hovered above the city. Casually selecting
sections of the city to destroy. Finding one she raised her hand
and a flash detonated it. The screams of thousands fleeing or
wounded echoed into the night. One by one more of Felwithe
vanished.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">*(End Track)</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Seeing another section she raised her hand
to destroy it. But a Silver haired boy appeared in front of her.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Leylia! Stop this! Wake up!!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Without a thought a mana bolt struck him and
sent him to the ground. But the boy managed to get back up and
this time he grabbed hold of her and began to shout in her face.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU DOING!!! WAKE UP
LEYLIA!!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">She struggled against his grasp, he was very
strong.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;DAMN IT! DONT YOU REMEMBER ANYTHING!
WAKE UP LEYLIA!!&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">She struggled harder and then the boy
slapped her hard across the face. The energy around her faded
away and she began to fall. The boy caught hold of her and
brought her down to the street. He cradled her for a moment then
he collapsed on top of her. His weight pressing on her.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">He began to weakly say something.
&#147;......Lia...your so....ong.....I hate this part......dont
worry.......be back....&#148; Then his weight was gone, and she
blacked out.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">-------------------------------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;That&#146;s what happened
Leylia.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Oh no.&#148;<br
style="mso-special-character:line-break">
<br style="mso-special-character:line-break">
&#147;I&#146;m sorry Leylia.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;So what is going to happen to
me?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">King Thearis looked pained again.
&#147;Execution. Tomorrow at noon&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Leylia didn&#146;t day anything she just
cried.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">------------------------------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Guard, you're dismissed.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Yes M&#146;lord&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">The door to her chamber open and Caerdwill
entered.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Is it time already?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Yes.&#148; He sat down beside her.
&#147;Leylia. I know what you did, wasn&#146;t your fault&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;It was my fault. I killed all those
people. I destroyed two cities. I deserve to die.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">To her surprise he slapped her, something he
had never done. &#147; Don&#146;t talk like that, you have
powers, that most people can&#146;t even dream about. They were
driven out of control by the same people who killed your mother
and devastated this continent 18 years ago. If any one is too
blame it is them. Which is why...&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Caerdwill turned away and faced the wall.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;You must go out and find your
destiny.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Caerdwill?&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Go child. Find out your past and push
on to the future. Go. Just remember, Where you go from here is
your choice, just know this once leave the confines of this city,
you can not return.&quot;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Thank you Caerdwill.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&#147;Good bye Leylia. Forge a great
future.&#148;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">----------------------------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">End Of this Chapter!</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">----------------------------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;----------------------------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Preview of Chapter 3 (Spoiler Alert!)</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">----------------------------------------</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;Leylia and Reyas now set off from the
continent of Faydwer and journey to Antonica. On her first step
to reclaiming her past. In the next chapter of The Shadow
Falls:Twilight Leylia, learns of the testing point of
Raziel&#146;s and Arorua&#146;s love . But her plans are cut
short and now she must fight for her life against the elite of
Neriak. Can she succeed in finding out about her past? Or will
her journey be ended in its infancy. Find out in the next
Chapter: Love and Twilight!</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
